WEBVTT

1
00:55:56.130 --> 00:55:58.100 
但即便是现在 他内心还是在排斥我
But, even now, he still wants to shut me out.

2
00:55:58.130 --> 00:56:01.040 
他没有排斥你 他信任你
He doesn't wanna shut you out. He trusts you.

3
00:56:01.070 --> 00:56:02.710 
那他为什么会找你来
Then why are you here?

4
00:56:02.740 --> 00:56:04.540 
这证明他爱你
It proves that he loves you.

5
00:56:05.910 --> 00:56:08.010 
霍普 看着我
Hope. Look at me.

6
00:56:09.710 --> 00:56:11.150 
我可以是牺牲品
I'm expendable.

7
00:56:11.750 --> 00:56:13.020 
这就是我来这里的原因
That's why I'm here.

8
00:56:14.580 --> 00:56:17.250 
你现在应该明白
You must have realized that by now.

9
00:56:17.290 --> 00:56:19.170 
是我穿着战服 而不是你穿
I mean, it's why I'm in the suit and you're not.

10
00:56:21.590 --> 00:56:23.530 
他宁愿输了这场战斗也不愿失去你
He would rather lose this fight than lose you.

11
00:56:25.630 --> 00:56:26.630 
真的…
Anyway...

